# Cursor Rules

## Context and Scope
- Treat `.ai/PROJECT_STRUCTURE.md`, `.ai/AGENT_CONTRACT.md`, and `.ai/rules.md` as mandatory context.
- Keep edits within governed folders and files.

## Process
- Use Plan Mode for complex changes.
- Ask for missing acceptance criteria when scope is ambiguous.
- Validate with tests/checks relevant to changed areas.

## Quality Gates
- Keep CI checks passing.
- Do not track local-only paths (`results/`, `logs/`, `tests/scripts/`).
- Update docs and checklist when behavior/policy/structure changes.
